IwYTFjOCIsImRpc3RyaWJ1dG9ySWQiOiI1NmIxZWI5MzQ0ZmVjYTNkZjJlMzIwY2IiLCJhcGlrZXlJZCI6IjU2YjFlZmVlMGNmMjEzYWQyMGRkMjE3MCJ9","attributeIdMultimediaContent":"IMAGE","attributeIdMultimediaContentDescription":"Image","attributeIdSizeOrientation":"16X9","width":"280","height":"158","altText":"Family Fun","caption":"Easter Races","photographer":"Ipswich Turf Club","copyright":"Ipswich Turf Club","sequenceNumber":"500"}],"openTimes":[],"productComments":[{"marketVariantId":"English / Global","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ENGLISH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"English","commentText":"Spend your Easter Monday trackside at Ipswich Turf Club.\n\nAn afternoon of live horse racing, fresh air and family fun. Best of all entry is free!\n\nBring the kids along and let them join the Easter Egg Hunt, held at the Grange Garden.\n\nRound up your friends, pack the family and enjoy a relaxed afternoon at the races this Easter Monday."},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Trascorri il Lunedì di Pasqua all'ippodromo di Ipswich Turf Club.\n\nUn pomeriggio di corse di cavalli dal vivo, aria fresca e divertimento per tutta la famiglia. E soprattutto, l'ingresso è gratuito!\n\nPorta i bambini e partecipa alla caccia alle uova di Pasqua, che si terrà al Grange Garden.\n\nRiunisci gli amici, porta tutta la famiglia e goditi un pomeriggio di relax alle corse questo Lunedì di Pasqua."},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"Pasa el Lunes de Pascua en el hipódromo del Ipswich Turf Club.\n\nUna tarde de carreras de caballos en vivo, aire fresco y diversión para toda la familia. ¡Y lo mejor de todo es que la entrada es gratuita!\n\nTrae a los niños y que participen en la búsqueda de huevos de Pascua, que se celebra en el Grange Garden.\n\nReúne a tus amigos, a toda la familia y disfruta de una tarde relajada en las carreras este Lunes de Pascua."},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Habiskan Senin Paskah Anda di pinggir lintasan pacuan kuda di Ipswich Turf Club.\n\nSore hari yang penuh dengan pacuan kuda langsung, udara segar, dan keseruan keluarga. Yang terbaik dari semuanya, masuknya gratis!\n\nAjak anak-anak Anda dan biarkan mereka bergabung dalam Perburuan Telur Paskah, yang diadakan di Grange Garden.\n\nKumpulkan teman-teman Anda, ajak keluarga Anda, dan nikmati sore yang santai di arena pacuan kuda pada Senin Paskah ini."},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"부활절 월요일 입스위치 경마장에서 즐거운 시간을 보내세요.\n\n신선한 공기 속에서 펼쳐지는 경마 경기와 가족 모두가 즐길 수 있는 오후입니다. 무엇보다 입장료가 무료입니다!\n\n아이들을 데리고 오셔서 그레인지 가든에서 열리는 부활절 달걀 찾기 행사에 참여하게 해 주세요.\n\n친구들과 가족들을 모아 이번 부활절 월요일 경마장에서 여유로운 오후를 만끽하세요."},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"イースターマンデーは、イプスウィッチ・ターフクラブの競馬場で過ごしませんか？\n\n午後は、迫力満点の競馬観戦、爽やかな空気、そして家族みんなで楽しめるアクティビティが満載です。しかも入場無料！\n\nお子様連れで、グランジガーデンで開催されるイースターエッグハントに参加させてあげましょう。\n\nお友達やご家族と一緒に、イースターマンデーは競馬場でゆったりとした午後をお過ごしください。"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"复活节星期一，来伊普斯维奇赛马俱乐部 (Ipswich Turf Club) 赛马场度过一个轻松愉快的下午吧！\n\n这里不仅有精彩的赛马比赛，还有清新的空气和阖家欢乐。最棒的是，入场免费！\n\n带上孩子们，让他们参加在格兰奇花园 (Grange Garden) 举行的复活节彩蛋寻宝活动。\n\n快约上朋友，带上家人，在这个复活节星期一，来伊普斯维奇赛马场享受一个轻松愉快的下午吧！"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"復活節星期一，來伊普斯維奇賽馬俱樂部 (Ipswich Turf Club) 賽馬場度過一個輕鬆愉快的下午吧！\n\n這裡不僅有精彩的賽馬比賽，還有清新的空氣和閔家歡樂。最棒的是，免費入場！\n\n帶上孩子們，讓他們參加在格蘭奇花園 (Grange Garden) 舉行的復活節彩蛋尋寶活動。\n\n快約朋友，帶上家人，在這個復活節星期一，來伊普斯維奇賽馬場享受一個輕鬆愉快的下午吧！"},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"Passe a sua segunda-feira de Páscoa no hipódromo do Ipswich Turf Club.\n\nUma tarde de corridas de cavalos ao vivo, ar puro e diversão para toda a família. E o melhor de tudo: a entrada é gratuita!\n\nTraga as crianças e deixe-as participar da Caça aos Ovos de Páscoa, que acontecerá no Grange Garden.\n\nReúna seus amigos, traga a família e aproveite uma tarde relaxante nas corridas nesta segunda-feira de Páscoa."},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Passez votre lundi de Pâques à l'hippodrome d'Ipswich Turf Club.\n\nUn après-midi de courses hippiques en direct, d'air frais et de divertissement en famille. Le meilleur ? L'entrée est gratuite !\n\nAmenez vos enfants et inscrivez-les à la chasse aux œufs de Pâques, organisée dans les jardins de Grange.\n\nRéunissez vos amis, emmenez votre famille et profitez d'un après-midi de détente aux courses ce lundi de Pâques."},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Verbringen Sie Ihren Ostermontag an der Rennbahn des Ipswich Turf Clubs.\n\nEin Nachmittag voller Live-Pferderennen, frischer Luft und Spaß für die ganze Familie. Und das Beste: Der Eintritt ist frei!\n\nBringen Sie Ihre Kinder mit und lassen Sie sie an der Ostereiersuche im Grange Garden teilnehmen.\n\nSchnappen Sie sich Ihre Freunde, packen Sie die Familie ein und genießen Sie einen entspannten Nachmittag auf der Rennbahn an diesem Ostermontag."}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"Ipswich Turf Club","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"219 Brisbane Road","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Bundamba","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4304","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.6153147","geocodeGdaLongitude":"152.8043706","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"mediaLinks":[],"alternateNames":[],"internationalReach":"","rates":[{"ratesType":"","ratesTypeDescription":"","priceFrom":"","priceTo":"","free":"true","rateComment":""}],"deals":[],"jobVacancies":[],"weather":"","menuUrl":"","winelistUrl":"","doesServeMeal":"","openingTime":{"openingTimeType":"","seasonalPeriods":[],"openingTimeComment":"","exceptions":{"exceptionPeriod":"","periods":[]}},"productProximity":[],"productWidget":[],"services":[],"verticalClassifications":[{"productTypeId":"SPORT","productTypeDescription":"Sporting Events"}],"pageURL":"/au/en/things-to-do/events/p-63fd3f366820aac341b0a1c8-easter-monday-races","classificationLayer":[{"attributeId":"sports-events"}]}}]},"disabledClassifications":["classes-and-workshops","participation-and-endurance","markets-and-community","business-event","food-and-wine","music-and-festivals"]}